Title: An Act Changing the Name of Sugal Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Manuel Medel, Sr. Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 753
An Act Changing the Name of Sugal Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao Del Sur, to Manuel Medel, Sr. Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Sugal Elementary School in the Municipality of Jose Abad Santos, Province of Davao del Sur, is changed to Manuel Medel, Sr. Elementary School.1avvphi1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: April 13, 1984
